headline: Nvidia CEO Downplays AI Bubble Fears as He Enlists New Partners
summary: The Blackwell processor, Nvidia’s flagship artificial intelligence accelerator, and the newer Rubin model are fueling an unprecedented surge of sales growth through 2026, Huang said Tuesday at a company presentation in Washington.
